    public class SsoServerTopologyMeta
extends com.sun.management.snmp.agent.SnmpMibGroup
implements Serializable, com.sun.management.snmp.agent.SnmpStandardMetaServer
    The class is used for representing SNMP metadata for the "SsoServerTopology" group. The group is defined with the following oid: 1.3.6.1.4.1.42.2.230.3.1.1.2.1.8.
